/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, giving a sense of the city's towering structures. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. The street itself is a hive of activity, with cars and buses moving along its length, adding a dynamic element to the scene. In the distance, power lines crisscross against the sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The image is bathed in the light of day, highlighting the colors and details of the cityscape.
